ge skipsbyggingsdivisjonen til nye eiere. Salget har latt vente p\u00e5 seg, men i forrige uke kunne kommunikasjonsdirekt\u00f8r \u00d8yvind Risnes fortelle at de er i sluttforhandlinger og at de regner med at Rissa-verftet kan f\u00e5 nye eiere allerede denne m\u00e5neden.", "LES MER: Sluttforhandlinger om Rissa-verft"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "5617e2c611dd1dffe1b04bf2925c78162c7d9288bfef9ce8c1122692934cf413"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-13T13:28:00.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Bergen Group krevde 61 millioner fra polsk verft, men tapte saken."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/okonomi/article7701587.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Stavangerfjord_20130606_0001.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ca4865848d98d6c39c0667e4c0450b59ecb2744b.jpg?594ee1e2"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Rissa-verft d\u00f8mt til \u00e5 betale 28 millioner -adressa.no", "Store forsinkelser", "Tapte saken", "Nye eiere p\u00e5 vei inn"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "ca4865848d98d6c39c0667e4c0450b59ecb2744b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "personal-finance"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "bergen group"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["saken", "millioner", "millioner kroner"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["stavangerfjord", "stocznia gdansk", "fjord line"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["stockholm", "rissa"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "valu